{"tid":2108194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[九東選民入]如果黃之鋒被DQ，你會唔會投佢既plan B梁凱晴呢？","createTime":"2020-07-14T11:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T00:33:34.000Z","uid":4521,"like":56,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e08749e4f3906d1cfd09889ba7154d2e170a74d","tid":2108194,"uid":4521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"會投梁凱晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會投梁凱晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之鋒作為DQ師其實都好大機會比政府DQ，問過身邊好多朋友，有人會轉投梁凱晴，有人不了。原因如下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會投plan B梁凱晴<br />\n1. 尊重初選協議，被DQ可以自己指派plan B頂上<br />\n2. 梁凱晴同之鋒呢幾個月都好努力<br />\n3. 梁凱晴係素人，可奶也<br />\n4. 靚女<br />\n5. 夠巴渣，可以入去鬧交<br />\n6. 相信之鋒眼光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不投plan B梁凱晴<br />\n1. 區都未做好就玩立會，韓國魚2.0<br />\n2. 唔夠重單手搬得走，無法增加議政成本<br />\n3. 突然彈出黎無咩個人賣點<br />\n4. 投比之鋒係認同之鋒工作，唔代表認同梁凱晴工作<br />\n5. 對其他候選人唔公平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利：初選有投票，不過未諗到會唔會投plan B<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2228442c60c87f66aaa9ab9e32a5c930a2ceab6","tid":2108194,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"我投大波<br />\n<br />\n因此李嘉達最好"},{"pid":"0a507b0fc641b9a686a4743fe1ebe32f2ffbf733","tid":2108194,"uid":30084,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"尊重初選協議 就唔好用PLAN B身份避開初選喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fcbf44c1a782a822df73236fb5071d13892d37","tid":2108194,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"月華選民<br />\n我比肥仔達都唔會佢"},{"pid":"a086d588ce226ff45e30de554331c0f4b4e44074","tid":2108194,"uid":4521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉今年9月舉行，劍指「35+」的各路民主派敲定最終初選方案，今日（9日）舉行記者會公布詳情。負責牽頭的港大法律系副教授戴耀廷坦言，港區國安法實施後，民主派被取消參選以至當選資格的機會非常大，若公民投票後獲推薦的參選人被取消資格，將會由該人指定「Plan B」出選。<br />\n<br />\nhk01慎入：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/483725/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8Cdq%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%A4%A7-%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%AE%9Aplan-b%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F483725%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%2580%25E5%25BB%25B7-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258Cdq%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25AE%259Aplan-b%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%25B8&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=7190c3eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/483725/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8Cdq%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%A4%A7-%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%AE%9Aplan-b%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8</a>"},{"pid":"429d982ae58244af3f3e2afb7cd601889818a8fa","tid":2108194,"uid":4521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66fcbf44c1a782a822df73236fb5071d13892d37","tid":2108194,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"月華選民<br />\n我比肥仔達都唔會佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"肥仔做區都未算好<br />\n不過係夠重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5745bc552561841ce938f3fb4a57a2c2bcf325","tid":2108194,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"晴B巴渣咩?"},{"pid":"70add30ea9505670ed9d594903f65d4e4c76c603","tid":2108194,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"429d982ae58244af3f3e2